      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a fair way to put it, but isn't it kind of hard to say it's \"necessary\" if it almost always ends up causing conflict or targeting minorities? it feels like the \"glue\" part is just a way to justify things that end up being pretty toxic in the long run. don't you think the negative side of it is actually the defining characteristic?",
